      "name": "General Steelstrike",
      "elite": true,
      "quotes": [
        {
          "soundId": 251210,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-118-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839999,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/127/5839999/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_118_F.ogg",
          "text": "By the light of the Flame! What is that fresh horror?",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251199,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-107-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839988,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/116/5839988/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_107_F.ogg",
          "text": "Down here, champion. The cultists have overrun the city.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251200,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-108-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839989,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/117/5839989/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_108_F.ogg",
          "text": "Find and defeat them, or we will have to face that commander at full strength.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251184,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-92-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839973,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/101/5839973/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_92_F.ogg",
          "text": "If the Order of Night steals the Dawnbreaker, Mereldar will be defenseless!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251204,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-112-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839993,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/121/5839993/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_112_F.ogg",
          "text": "Luckily, my daughter and her children are safe. You've weakened the commander and cleansed my home. Thank you.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251194,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-102-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839983,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/111/5839983/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_102_F.ogg",
          "text": "Only one more ship and the Dawnbreaker is ours again!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251213,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-121-f",
          "fileDataId": 5840002,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/130/5840002/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_121_F.ogg",
          "text": "That creature of theirs has fled back to their queen. No doubt with tales of your fearsome heroism.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251202,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-110-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839991,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/119/5839991/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_110_F.ogg",
          "text": "They try to defile our faith. Instead you have weakened their commander.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251187,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-95-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839976,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/104/5839976/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_95_F.ogg",
          "text": "They've got us surrounded. You'll need to use those mounts of yours to fly to them.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251208,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-116-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839997,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/125/5839997/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_116_F.ogg",
          "text": "Wait. No! They've sent a force back up and retaken the Dawnbreaker!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251206,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-114-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839995,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/123/5839995/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_114_F.ogg",
          "text": "We've weakened the nerubian's foothold on the town and their commander.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251212,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-120-f",
          "fileDataId": 5840001,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/129/5840001/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_120_F.ogg",
          "text": "You've done it, champion! You've broken the unholy alliance between the Order of Night and Azj-Kahet.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251207,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-115-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839996,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/124/5839996/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_115_F.ogg",
          "text": "You've saved Mereldar, champion. We'll drive the remainder of this shadowy lot from the city.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 252024,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-142-f",
          "fileDataId": 5859525,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/197/5859525/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_142_F.ogg",
          "text": "Our airship engineers are running dangerously low on supplies. Recover what tools you can.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251197,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-105-f",
