          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/114/5839986/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_105_F.ogg",
          "text": "Three nerubian lieutenants are empowering the commander who leads them.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251198,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-106-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839987,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/115/5839987/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_106_F.ogg",
          "text": "We must liberate the city. We need your help, outsider--no. Champion.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251196,
          "filename": "vo-110-vaelisia-steelstrike-104-f",
          "fileDataId": 5839985,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/113/5839985/VO_110_Vaelisia_Steelstrike_104_F.ogg",
